 The Olubadan of Ibadan, Oba Saliu Adetunji, has joined his ancestors. Reports said he died in the early hours of today at the University College Hospital, Ibadan, after an illness. His death was also confirmed by the Ekarun Olubadan, High Chief Amidu Ajibade. The late Oba Adetunji became the Olubadan on March 4, 2016. Details laterâ€¦ 